Cell["\<\
You will most likely get 0... It is essentially impossible to land at random \
on any specific random real... Real numbers are a complicated set.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.779695743698213*^9, 
  3.779695794050582*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"56ecdfcd-1971-4123-aeb8-\
77bad3d09431"]
}, Open  ]],

